  "description": "<i>Dragonia</i> is a multi-scene icon-driven RPG/adventure game with puzzle elements. The player can control the movements of the character by keyboard or Sinclair joystick following the four main compass directions, and also his actions by scrolling and selecting or combining the icons on the interface of the screen. <br><br>Each icon represents an action such as picking/dropping objects, talk, use, wear, pray, and listen among others. The last one is of particular use for the awareness of the player, in case menace is present in the surroundings of the scenario. The game may also be saved and later loaded by using specific icons. The player may assemble several spells or weaponry which will be prove to be useful during his quest.<br><br>The player plays as Cebrenia, an apprentice wizard who has to prove himself to the Elder wizards by completing a dangerous quest. He has to find the magical Golden Crown, symbol of freedom and peace on the doomed city of Dragonia within a limit of time.",
